<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= home.HouseName %> | Home Details</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /* --- General Body and Font Styling (Dark Theme) --- */
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #1a202c; /* Dark blue-grey background */
      color: #cccccc; /* Light grey for default text */
    }

    /* --- Main Container (Dark Theme) --- */
    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: #282c34; /* Darker card background */
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      border: 1px solid #444; /* Subtle border for dark theme */
    }

    /* --- Home Image Styling --- */
    .home-image {
      width: 100%;
      height: 400px;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    /* --- Details Section (Dark Theme) --- */
    .details {
      padding: 40px;
    }

    .details h1 {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 38px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #61dafb; /* Vibrant light blue for heading */
    }

    /* --- Information Grid Styling (Dark Theme) --- */
    .info-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 25px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      padding: 25px;
      background-color: #21252b; /* Slightly different dark shade for offset */
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid #444;
    }

    .info-grid p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #cccccc;
    }

    .info-grid p strong {
      display: block;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #00aaff; /* A strong blue for labels */
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    /* --- Description Styling (Dark Theme) --- */
    .description {
      margin-top: 30px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #cccccc;
    }

    .description p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .description p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    /* --- Buttons Section (Dark Theme) --- */
    .btns {
      margin-top: 40px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .btns a, .btns button {
      padding: 12px 28px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    /* Secondary Action: Back Link */
    .btns a {
      background-color: transparent;
      color: #61dafb;
      border-color: #61dafb;
    }

    .btns a:hover {
      background-color: #61dafb;
      color: #1a202c; /* Dark text on hover */
    }

    /* Primary Action: Book Now Button */
    .btns button {
      background-color: #26a69a; /* Vibrant teal/aqua color */
      color: white;
      border-color: #26a69a;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(38, 166, 154, 0.25);
    }

    .btns button:hover {
      background-color: #2bbbad;
      border-color: #2bbbad;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(38, 166, 154, 0.4);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <img src="https://picsum.photos/1000/450?random=2" alt="Home Image" class="home-image">

    <div class="details">
      <h1><%= home.HouseName %></h1>

      <div class="info-grid">
        <p><strong>Owned by:</strong> <%= home.OwnerName %></p>
        <p><strong>Location:</strong> <%= home.Location %></p>
        <p><strong>Price per night:</strong> ₹<%= home.Rate %></p>
        <p><strong>Rating:</strong> ⭐ <%= home.Rating %> / 5</p>
      </div>

      <div class="description">
        <p>Welcome to <strong><%= home.HouseName %></strong>, your perfect getaway destination! Nestled in the heart of <%= home.location %>, this stunning property combines modern design with a cozy ambiance to make you feel right at home.</p>
        <p>Enjoy peaceful mornings on the private balcony, relax in spacious and beautifully decorated rooms, and take advantage of all the premium amenities including high-speed Wi-Fi, a fully equipped kitchen, and 24/7 support. Whether you’re traveling solo, as a couple, or with family, this space is tailored for comfort and convenience.</p>
        <p>Book now to experience unforgettable stays, top-rated service, and a home you'll want to return to again and again.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="btns">
        <a href="/">← Back to Listings</a>
        <button>Book Now</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  
  <%-include('partials/footer')%>
</body>
</html>